{"tid":1792384,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[求推] 民陣同岑子杰唔該入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-12-21T15:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T18:28:52.000Z","uid":301388,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a8fa1b90e54bbe81c775b063fbd4358c6902ff35","tid":1792384,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又話叫人預留一月一號出嚟？</span></span></strong><br />\n宜家都廿幾號啦 點解仲係無乜聲氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係想催你地 不過得返一個禮拜多啲<br />\n文宣都要時間整圖、貼牆 (尤其是宜家一埋牆就俾狗圍)<br />\n如果想谷人數嘅話 宜家要開始做嘢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就住宜家嘅時勢，想谷人出嚟就要不停炒熱呢啲議題：<br />\n- 星火俾中共屈洗黑錢<br />\n- 教育界白色恐怖 (遲啲仲會燒到社福界、醫護界...)<br />\n- Connect 埋東突厥<br />\n- 當然仲有中共最唔想面對嘅721、831、101... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc018a8a0ca42209d9934070542c06fe6d3bd56","tid":1792384,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"721 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dceb37440981fa33af2caf1520ed59c04f9b8d71","tid":1792384,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"831 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e49c4af600059a1db4222f44f16752ea371301","tid":1792384,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:15:40.000Z","msg":"101 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e180d27a054e8df8aa25ba5cfc852987da1d8a","tid":1792384,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0